comments: Mitchell (UTA) and Markkanen (CHI) engage and disengage with one another after the screen.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Ingles' (UTA) path and makes marginal contact with his side as the pick is set.
LaVine (CHI) turns into Bogdanovic (UTA) and initiates contact with his side/left arm during his upward shooting motion.
Dunn (CHI) makes a slight brush to Gobert's (UTA) arm on the play to the basket.
Gobert (UTA) makes marginal body contact with Carter Jr. (CHI) as he attempts to gain control of the pass in the lane.
Carter Jr. (CHI) moves slightly into Gobert (UTA) and makes marginal contact with Gobert's side/front prior to starting his upward shooting motion.
Mitchell (UTA) makes contact across Carter Jr.'s (CHI) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Satoransky (CHI) rests his left hand/forearm against Ingles' (UTA) front as he drives toward the lane and makes marginal contact.
Mitchell (UTA) and Dunn (CHI) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another after Dunn gains control of the rebound.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (UTA) path and does not deliver the contact.
Bogdanovic (UTA) reflexively places his arm around Carter Jr.'s (CHI) upper half as the pick is set and quickly removes it.
Gobert (UTA) is retreating his right arm into a vertical position as he absorbs the contact initiated by LaVine (CHI) on the play to the basket.
LaVine (CHI) commits the take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and does not deliver the contact.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes marginal contact with Gobert's (UTA) backside as he simultaneously uses his right hand/arm to tie Gobert up. A jump ball is correctly assessed.
Gobert (UTA) maintains legal guarding position as LaVine (CHI) initiates the contact during his upward shooting motion. Gobert then cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) makes marginal contact with Carter Jr.'s (CHI) right arm/side prior to making clean contact with the ball during the inbound.
